void otPlatRadioClearExtSrcMatchAddressEntries(otInstance *aInstance);
  `
    MAC layer interface:
    `
void EnableSrcMatch(bool aEnable);
ThreadError AddSrcMatchAddressEntry(Address &aAddr);
ThreadError ClearSrcMatchAddressEntry(Address &aAddr);
`

2) OT will enable auto pend feature by default.

3) OT is aware of current status of queued messages for SED and will add one entry into hardware table for each SED which has queued messages. When no available entry for the hardware table, auto pend feature will be disabled and FramePending will be set for each ACK. Auto pend feature will be restored when there is no more queued indirect messages.

